headline.main: EU Says to Beef Up Climate Diplomacy to Save Paris Agreement
headline.print_headline: EU Says to Beef Up Climate Diplomacy to Save Paris Agreement

lead_paragraph: EU foreign ministers on Monday said the bloc would strengthen diplomacy to promote the fight against climate change in the face of a possible U.S. exit from the Paris agreement.
